00:22:28,220 --> 00:22:34,220
[SPEAKER_05] Što je vjerojatno vrlo utjecalo naročito na članove komisije.

209
00:22:34,220 --> 00:22:38,220
[SPEAKER_00] Miroslav Šutej worked in tandem with Vilko Žiljak.

210
00:22:38,220 --> 00:22:40,220
[SPEAKER_00] Both have had impressive careers.

211
00:22:40,220 --> 00:22:46,220
[SPEAKER_00] Painter, graphic artist, and designer Šutej designed the flag and coat of arms of the Republic of Croatia,

212
00:22:46,220 --> 00:22:48,220
