213
00:22:48,220 --> 00:22:56,220
[SPEAKER_00] Vilko Žiljak is a pioneer of mathematical modeling and simulation, computer graphics and visual computer research.

214
00:22:56,220 --> 00:23:06,220
[SPEAKER_13] Gospodin Šutej, znači moj kolega prijatelj je umjetnik po osnovnom svom opredjeljenju.

